  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vaporware Odyssey is a action roguelike inspired by vaporwave and synthwave aesthetics. It blends souls-like and bullet hell mechanics to create a uniquely action packed experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ <strong>Procedurally generated levels</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every room in the game is procedurally generated on a hex grid. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras/62db197c31809c9a9b13fc77cc0e87a6.avif?t=1741629040\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆  <strong>Synergetic Upgrades</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most upgrades are designed to synergies in fun and useful ways. There is almost always more then one way to combine upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras/81564cafedd6ed39d96f425849114f50.avif?t=1741629040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras_big/81564cafedd6ed39d96f425849114f50.avif?t=1741629040 width=800 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras/1a4648ed6b746ab43a45e70780ce7392.avif?t=1741629040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras_big/1a4648ed6b746ab43a45e70780ce7392.avif?t=1741629040 width=800 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras/43d4136d85adeab5c48da48ed45cb991.avif?t=1741629040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras_big/43d4136d85adeab5c48da48ed45cb991.avif?t=1741629040 width=800 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ Intense combat focused on <strong>dodging and jumping</strong> to avoid enemy attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras/04b3304190d116958424bf3a8a5ca9de.avif?t=1741629040\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vaporware Odyssey is a action roguelike inspired by vaporwave and synthwave aesthetics. It blends souls-like and bullet hell mechanics to create a uniquely action packed experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ <strong>Procedurally generated levels</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every room in the game is procedurally generated on a hex grid. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras/62db197c31809c9a9b13fc77cc0e87a6.avif?t=1741629040\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆  <strong>Synergetic Upgrades</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most upgrades are designed to synergies in fun and useful ways. There is almost always more then one way to combine upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras/81564cafedd6ed39d96f425849114f50.avif?t=1741629040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras_big/81564cafedd6ed39d96f425849114f50.avif?t=1741629040 width=800 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras/1a4648ed6b746ab43a45e70780ce7392.avif?t=1741629040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras_big/1a4648ed6b746ab43a45e70780ce7392.avif?t=1741629040 width=800 height=92 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729660/extras/43d4136d85adeab5c48da48ed45cb991.avif?t=1741629040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite